    "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/sgl-project/sglang/issues/12295",
    "number": 12295,
    "state": "closed",
    "locked": false,
    "title": "fix seqlen bug for trtllm_mla's draft_extend",
    "user": {
      "login": "bmac3",
      "id": 55830617,
      "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjU1ODMwNjE3",
      "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/55830617?v=4",
      "gravatar_id": "",
      "url": "https://api.github.com/users/bmac3",
      "html_url": "https://github.com/bmac3",
      "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bmac3/followers",
      "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bmac3/following{/other_user}",
      "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bmac3/gists{/gist_id}",
      "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bmac3/starred{/owner}{/repo}",
      "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bmac3/subscriptions",
      "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bmac3/orgs",
      "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bmac3/repos",
      "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bmac3/events{/privacy}",
      "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bmac3/received_events",
      "type": "User",
      "user_view_type": "public",
      "site_admin": false
    },
    "body": "In trtllm_mla's draft extend, we have `seq_lens = forward_batch.seq_lens.to(torch.int32)` which is passed to`flashinfer.decode.trtllm_batch_decode_with_kv_cache_mla`. `forward_batch.seq_lens.to(torch.int32)` does not take into account the padding we do to the queries with `pad_draft_extend_query`. This leads to mismatched q's and kv's when we call `flashinfer.decode.trtllm_batch_decode_with_kv_cache_mla`. We should instead have\r\n```\r\nseq_lens = (\r\n    forward_batch.seq_lens\r\n    - metadata.seq_lens_q\r\n    + metadata.max_seq_len_q\r\n).to(torch.int32)\r\n```\r\nto account for the padding.",
    "created_at": "2025-10-28T21:43:24Z",
    "updated_at": "2025-10-28T21:47:47Z",
    "closed_at": "2025-10-28T21:47:47Z",
    "merged_at": "2025-10-28T21:47:47Z",
    "merge_commit_sha": "8d6ab1cb88b5d00ea67a67df01b4077e23a489fe",
